summary: The long and strange story about how I acquired  TABINOF
body:
The long and strange story about how I acquired TABINOF

I had been really wanting tabinof and dapgo for long time (along with other youtuber books). Whenever I entered a bookshop I would always be low key looking for it, even if I was with family and wouldn’t be able to buy it, I at least wanted to see it irl. I’m only 13 so I couldn’t really go out and buy it on my own, and out of social anxiety and sheer embarrassment, asking for it was also out of the picture. I had basically given up all hope.

Until, when I was doing my whole low key looking for tabinof thing, I actually found it. For once I had actually seen it, and had the opportunity to buy it. But here’s the problem, I was in the biggest shopping centre in the county, WITH MY FAMILY, and had left all my money in the car. I didn’t even get a chance to look through it since the shop was crowded, so I just ruled out all hope once more. Though I didn’t want to truly give up, again.

The plan went like this:

I go down, find my mum and ask her if I can look around on my own, she agrees and I go, buy a backpack in superdry (I needed one anyways so it was a reasonable purchase) go up to the shop, buy the book (among others) get the bag that they are in and put them in the backpack, go to holister and buy something so I don’t look suspicious, get the keys to my mums car, take the bag with the books out and into the boot (covered by coats) , return to the shopping centre, go back to my family and act like I only bought the two things.

And, to my surprise, it worked!

I was also staying in my grandparents house for a few days, and my house is about four hours away, so I can’t take them out of the boot until I go home.

And all this was to avoid being embarrassed.
